Package: ergmito
Version: 0.1-0
Date: 2018-09-24
Title: Exponential Random Graph Models for Small Networks
Description: The package implements simulation and estimation algorithms for 
  Exponential Random Graph Models in the case of small networks using exact
  statistics. As a difference from the 'ergm' package, 'ergmito' skips the
  MCMC part of the estimation process and goes straight to MLE.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
